# The contextual keywords `empty`, `member`, `of`, and `a` are recognized as predicate words only
# immediately after `is` (spec/grammar.md:230); elsewhere they remain ordinary names. None of them
# are in the reserved-word set, so they are usable as a variable name, a call name, or an
# assignment target with no diagnostics.
print :empty
print member
print of
:a = 5
